<% content_for :title, "About Us | Newpage Integrity Travels & Tours" %>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative py-20 bg-brand-blue-dark overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1454165804606-c3d57bc86b40?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Corporate Team" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-20 mix-blend-overlay">
  </div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h1 class="font-heading text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">About Newpage Integrity</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-brand-blue-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Your trusted partner in navigating global opportunities with excellence and transparency.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Company History & Mission -->
<section class="py-20 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div>
        <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-brand-gray-900 mb-6">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
          Founded with a vision to simplify international travel, education, and business processes, Newpage Integrity Travels & Tours Limited has grown into a leading consulting firm in Nigeria. We recognized the challenges individuals and businesses face when dealing with complex visa applications, university admissions, and corporate registrations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Our goal has always been to provide a transparent, efficient, and highly professional service that removes the stress from these processes. Today, we pride ourselves on our high success rates and the hundreds of satisfied clients who have achieved their dreams through our guidance.
        </p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-brand-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-brand-blue">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-brand-gray-900 mb-2">Our Mission</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">To provide seamless, reliable, and transparent travel, educational, and corporate services that empower our clients to achieve their global aspirations.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-brand-gray-50 p-6 rounded-xl border-l-4 border-brand-red">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-brand-gray-900 mb-2">Our Vision</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">To be the most trusted and preferred consulting agency in Africa for travel, immigration, and business solutions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-brand-blue transform translate-x-4 translate-y-4 rounded-2xl opacity-10"></div>
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1552664730-d307ca884978?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Team Meeting" class="relative rounded-2xl shadow-xl w-full">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Core Values -->
<section class="py-20 bg-brand-gray-50">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl font-bold text-brand-gray-900 mb-4">Our Core Values</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500">The principles that guide our every action and decision.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-soft text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-blue/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-brand-blue">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-brand-gray-900 mb-3">Integrity</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500">It's in our name. We operate with complete honesty, transparency, and ethical standards in all client dealings.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-soft text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-brand-red/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-brand-red">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-brand-gray-900 mb-3">Excellence</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500">We strive for perfection in our service delivery, constantly updating our knowledge to provide the best guidance.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-soft text-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6 text-green-600">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-xl text-brand-gray-900 mb-3">Client-Centric</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-500">Your success is our success. We tailor our services to meet your specific needs and ensure your satisfaction.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="py-20 bg-brand-blue">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <h2 class="font-heading text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-6">Ready to Start Your Journey?</h2>
    <p class="text-brand-blue-100 text-lg mb-8">Contact us today for a free consultation and let us help you turn your travel or business dreams into reality.</p>
    <%= link_to "Get in Touch", contact_path, class: "inline-block bg-white text-brand-blue font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full shadow-lg hover:bg-gray-50 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300" %>
  </div>
</section>
